{"tid":1216881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你有你遊行，我去海洋公園玩得好開心，吹咩？","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:12:55.000Z","uid":260252,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"11442eb87c9727d42aa0baa28771b6241a1d2e15","tid":1216881,"uid":260252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7w306Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7w306Z.png&h=e29af5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEw7Jkm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEw7Jkm.png&h=1f0bae3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呀屋企兩老等我啲錢開飯<br />\n所以我決定俾錢去海洋公園玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋班人示威就好啦，唔好阻到我去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀6月12號，海洋公園不見不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋有你嘅立場，香港搞成點我冇所謂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢見到我12號去咗海洋公園"},{"pid":"c25cf1d96f3a7bc618b28409eb47a54406402c0d","tid":1216881,"uid":142518,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"你冇立場冇問題<br />\n但至少可唔可以唔好喺一班義士受傷流血<br />\n抗爭嘅時候post埋一啲玩樂相呢<br />\n你有權唔支持我哋做嘅嘢，但你亦都可以選擇沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事不關己高高掛起，你冇權享受我哋爭取返嚟嘅嘢"},{"pid":"cd65c3701ee3d7815929711f6a8926913a630397","tid":1216881,"uid":260252,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"c25cf1d96f3a7bc618b28409eb47a54406402c0d","tid":1216881,"uid":142518,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"你冇立場冇問題<br />\n但至少可唔可以唔好喺一班義士受傷流血<br />\n抗爭嘅時候post埋一啲玩樂相呢<br />\n你有權唔支持我哋做嘅嘢，但你亦都可以選擇沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事不關己高高掛起，你冇權享受我哋爭取返嚟嘅嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"關唔關我事呀<img src=\"/ass